nhc_headline: ...DEPRESSION FORECAST TO STRENGTHEN DURING THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS...
summary: ...DEPRESSION FORECAST TO STRENGTHEN DURING THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS... As of 8:00 PM MST Sun Aug 24 the center of Ten-E was located near 16.5, -110.6 with movement WNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1005 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
